ary     murray charles august   real education aei archived from the original on january   retrieved january     where are the female einsteins   adviser to texas gop’s greg abbott no ‘evidence’ that women are ‘significant thinkers’ wwwrawstorycom   murray charles  back cover review what is intelligence beyond the flynn effect expanded paperback ed cambridge cambridge university press p back cover isbn  retrieved october   lay summary october     charles murray questions azusa pacific inside higher ed retrieved october     jaschik scott charles murray questions azusa pacific  inside higher ed wwwinsidehigheredcom retrieved  february    murray charles charles murray an open letter to the students of azusa pacific university aei ideas american enterprise institute retrieved october     a b speakers november   archived from the original on november     jewish genius commentarymagazinecom retrieved january     freedom to marry freedom to dissent why we must have both   keychainmail march   middlebury students college administrator and staff assault students endanger lives after murray protest middbeat retrieved march     statement from president laurie l patton regarding charles murray event middlebury college march     staff writers march   middlebury college professor injured by protesters as she escorted controversial speaker addison county independent addison county vermont retrieved  march    hallenbeck brent march   protesters created violent incident at middlebury burlington free press retrieved march     murray charles march   charles murray into the middle of a mob – what happened when i tried to speak at middlebury foxnewscom retrieved march     opinions the middlebury campus retrieved march     middlebury college completes sanctioning process for march  disruptions middlebury college  retrieved    reilly katie may   middlebury has sanctioned students for shutting down charles murrays lecture time retrieved may     lozado carlos may   the case for conservative